        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository a326595c-bf01-431a-b8c4-abccadc8a2ad).Image",
        "Description": "It&#39;s spring cleaning time in Berlin. Shut down the ongoing drug operation in a loud and spectacular way using different types of Bartoli Shotguns to kill 4 targets tied to selling and buying drugs in the club. Do not pacify anyone and use only weapons you bring with you or find lying around.\r\rBartoli Hunting Shotgun and Tactical Bartoli 12G can be found on the map lying around.\rBartoli 12 Short H can be unlocked by reaching Mumbai Mastery lvl 5.\rSawed Off Bartoli 12G can be unlocked by reaching New York Mastery lvl 13 but it can also be found in the club if you speak to a right person.\r\rStealing Sawed Off from bikers won&#39;t work here.",
